Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:05.48,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WELCOME TO STRAIGHT FROM THE HEART BECAUSE\NHVAC CLEANING SHOULD BE A POSITIVE EXPERIENCE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:08.16,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I'M HERE WITH DAVID HART, FOUNDER OF RAM\NAIR.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.16,0:00:09.48,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,DAVID, HOW ARE DOING TODAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:11.49,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,GREAT, THANKS, MORNING DAVE, HOW YOU DOING?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:12.74,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WHAT'S GOING ON IN OREGON?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.72,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WHAT'S HAPPENING THIS WEEK?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:15.86,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,KEEPIN' BUSY?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.86,0:00:17.60,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S MEMORIAL DAY WEEKEND.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.60,0:00:20.25,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND THIS IS A RESORT TOWN HERE IN BEND WHERE\NI LIVE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:22.09,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO IT IS PACKED OUT THERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:23.25,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,BUT YEAH.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.55,0:00:29.77,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WELL, LISTEN, TODAY WE'RE GONNA TALK ABOUT\NUH HVAC CLEANING SHOULD BE PART OF ANY RESTORATION PROJECT, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.77,0:00:38.67,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,UH IT SEEMS LIKE AXIOMATIC, LIKE OF COURSE,\NBUT TALK TO ME WHY PEOPLE DON'T THINK THAT WAY AND WHY WOULD THEY SHOULD THINK THAT WAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:48.40,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU KNOW, THIS IS SOMETHING UM THAT BECOMES\NMORE AND MORE OF SOMETHING ABOUT WHICH WE TALK AS AN INDUSTRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:54.82,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU KNOW, I'VE BEEN DOING THIS FOR LIKE 30\NYEARS IN THE CLEANING AND RESTORATION INDUSTRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:00:56.63,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,STARTED RAM AIR 18 YEARS AGO.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.63,0:01:00.08,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THAT'S WHEN POSITIVE AIR DECK CLEANING WAS\NBORN, ACTUALLY 18 YEARS AGO.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:05.76,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND MORE AND MORE, ALL THE TIME, I'M FINDING\NTHIS TOPIC COMING UP FINALLY.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.76,0:01:15.55,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THE RESTORATION INDUSTRY IS WAKING UP TO THE\NFACT THAT, YEAH, WE NEED TO INCLUDE THE LUNGS OF THE BUILDING INTO THE RESTORATION PROCESS.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.03,0:01:17.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU KNOW, I GO TO AROUND.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.42,0:01:21.66,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,LIKE THEY WOULD CLEAN THE WHOLE PLACE, BUT\NTHEN LEAVE HVAC ALONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,0:01:22.72,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I MEAN, IS THAT EVEN POSSIBLE?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:23.90,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WHY WOULD THEY DO THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:32.76,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WELL, UH THE EXPERIENCE CONVENTION IN LAS\NVEGAS, WHICH IS THE BIGGEST CLEANING AND RESTORATION CONVENTION IN THE UNITED STATES, POSSIBLY EVEN THE WORLD EVERY YEAR, IT'S IN
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:34.13,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,LAS VEGAS COMING UP THIS SEPTEMBER.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:44.24,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IN FACT, UH I DID A PRESENTATION A COUPLE\NYEARS AGO ON THIS TOPIC AND IT WAS ALL RESTORERS AND CLEANERS OUT IN THE AUDIENCE.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:53.88,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND I JUST, I DON'T EVEN KNOW IF THEY KNEW\NTHAT MY TOPIC WAS HVAC AT THIS POINT, BECAUSE WHAT THE NAME OF THE PRESENTATION WAS PANEL OF EXPERTS.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:54.76,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THERE WERE FIVE OF US.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:02:01.19,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THERE WAS UH TWO PHDS, JEFF JONES, UH BARRY\NCOSTA, AND MYSELF.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:15.02,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND AS SOON AS I GOT UP ON THE STAGE, I\NASKED THE AUDIENCE, SAID, WHAT IN YOUR EXPERIENCE IS THE MOST IGNORED OR IMPROPERLY DONE PORTION OF EVERY RESTORATION JOB YOU'VE EVER KNOWN?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:19.08,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND LOT OF HANDS WENT UP AND I STARTED\NPOINTING TO PEOPLE, HVAC, HVAC, HVAC.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:21.93,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT WAS THE ONLY ANSWER, AND IT'S THE CORRECT\NANSWER.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:25.99,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S BEEN THE MOST IGNORED PORTION.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.13,0:02:33.27,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,MOST RESTORATION JOBS THAT I'VE BEEN ON\NPRIOR TO MY GETTING INVOLVED IN IT, THE HVAC WASN'T EVEN DONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:35.43,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND THAT DOESN'T MAKE ANY SENSE.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.43,0:02:36.73,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S PART OF THE STRUCTURE.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.73,0:02:42.37,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,NOW, AT MICROBIAL WARRIOR, WE ALWAYS MENTION\NSTRUCTURE AND CONTENTS, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:44.78,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND INDOOR AIR QUALITY, THOSE THREE THINGS,\NRIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:48.58,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,NOW, THE INDOOR AIR QUALITY, OF COURSE, IS\NLARGELY AFFECTED BY THE STRUCTURE AND CONTENTS.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:50.93,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,BUT WHAT IS THE HVAC?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:55.05,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THE HVAC IS PART OF THE STRUCTURE AND IT'S\NALSO A CONTENT.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:03:02.81,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND IT'S THE PORTION OF THE STRUCTURE\NRESPONSIBLE FOR MOVING THE AIR THROUGHOUT THE ENTIRE STRUCTURE.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:05.13,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,NOW WHEN YOU'RE MOVING THE AIR, WHAT ELSE\NARE YOU MOVING?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.13,0:03:06.27,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WHATEVER'S IN THE AIR.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:07.87,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU'RE MOVING CONTAMINANTS.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:18.75,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO TO NOT INCLUDE IT ON EVERY SINGLE\NRESTORATION JOB, WHETHER IT BE SMOKE, CRIME SCENE, UNINTENDED DEATH, HOMICIDE, SUICIDE, ILLICIT DRUG, MOLD.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:21.84,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,UH YOU'RE JUST NOT DOING THE JOB COMPLETELY.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:25.13,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WHY WASN'T IT DONE BEFORE?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:27.87,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IS IT BECAUSE THEY JUST DIDN'T HAVE THE\NEQUIPMENT?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:29.30,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THAT'S NOT WHAT THEY DO?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:32.12,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,OR THEY COULDN'T BILL FOR IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:35.49,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S EXTRA WORK, IT WOULDN'T BE UH CHARGED\NTHROUGH INSURANCE?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:37.85,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WHAT WAS THE PRIMARY REASON?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:39.25,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YEAH.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.31,0:03:40.76,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YEAH.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:44.53,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I'M GOING TO START WITH THE MOST RECENT ONE\NYOU SAID, AND THAT WAS THE BILLING POINTS.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:50.32,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,UH XACTIMATE, A LOT OF RESTORATION\NCOMPANIES, DARE I SAY MOST, GO WITH XACTIMATE.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:57.88,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND UH UNTIL RECENTLY, THERE WAS ONLY TWO\NXACTIMATE LINE ITEMS FOR HVAC CLEANING AND DECONTAMINATION.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:06.73,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,NOW, BOB JORDAN, WHO WAS WITH THE UH ONE OF\NOUR INTERVIEWS, UH HE AND I WORKED TOGETHER ON DOUBLING THE NUMBER OF
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:09.71,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,LINE ITEMS IN XACTIMATE FOR HVAC.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:12.85,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO FROM TWO TO FOUR, OKAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:15.48,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,BUT THAT'S STILL HECK OF A LOT BETTER.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.33,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,CAN GET PAID FOR THE WORK YOU DO.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:19.75,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU AND ANY, YEAH, YEAH.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:21.33,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,GET PAID WELL.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:27.52,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THAT'S A LET'S TOUCH ON THAT BECAUSE THAT'S\NVERY IMPORTANT I WANT TO TOUCH ON THAT BUT BUT MORE TO YOUR MOST RECENT QUESTION.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:29.53,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WHY HAS IT BEEN IGNORED?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:41.06,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I THINK A LOT OF IT IS ALSO OUT OF SIGHT OUT\NOF MIND YOU KNOW WHEN YOU SEE UH SOMEBODY AND THEY GOT SKIN CANCER YOU KNOW IT YOU CAN SEE IT OR LIP CANCER ANYTHING LIKE THIS LUNG
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:46.30,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,CANCER THEY CAN'T SEE YOU KNOW AND THAT LIKE\NI SAY IT IS THE LUNGS OF THE BUILDING.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.61,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S VERY IMPORTANT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:52.69,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,ONE MIGHT EVEN SAY THAT THE LUNGS ARE UH ONE\NOF THE MOST IMPORTANT PARTS OF THE BODY.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:56.03,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WELL, THE HVAC SYSTEM IS ONE OF THE MOST\NIMPORTANT PARTS OF THE STRUCTURE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:05:01.99,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I THINK IT'S BEEN A COMBINATION OF, FIRST OF\NALL, THERE HASN'T BEEN THE METHODOLOGY IN ORDER TO DO IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:15.66,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,UH THE TRADITIONAL WAY OF CLEANING HVAC\NSYSTEMS UH HAS BEEN SHOWN TO EXACERBATE THE ISSUE BECAUSE IT'S PULLING UH
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:18.78,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,MAKEUP AIR FROM THE STRUCTURE INTO THE DUCTS\NAS IT'S DOING IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:20.28,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU JUST, NEVER CATCH UP.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.62,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU'RE CONSTANTLY RECONTAMINATING WHAT\NYOU'RE CLEANING.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:28.62,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO UNTIL VERY RECENTLY, WITHIN THE LAST\NYEAR, THE METHODOLOGY HASN'T BEEN ADOPTED.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:41.19,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,NOW, WHEN JEFF JONES OF MICROBIAL WARRIOR\NASKED ME TO WRITE THE STANDARDS AND COME UP WITH THE METHODOLOGY FOR A FORENSIC RESTORATION OF HVAC UH IN WHICH MOLD FALLS BECAUSE, YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:42.60,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,KNOW, IT'S A BIOCONTAMINANT.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:44.00,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,UH
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:57.38,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WE CAME INTO THIS VERY ROOM RIGHT HERE, MY\NLAB ASSISTANT AND I, AND WE SPENT TWO MONTHS AND WE JUST HAMMERED OUT M THE PROCESS FOR DECONTAMINATION RECHECK AND WE NAILED IT, MADE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:58.48,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT BULLETPROOF.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:02.60,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND WHAT ARE RESTORATION PROFESSIONALS\NSAYING NOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:13.23,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,NOW THAT THEY'RE GETTING, THEY HAVE THE\NXACTIMATE CODES, NOW THAT IT'S BECOMING MORE EXPECTED TO CLEAN THE LUNGS OF THE BUILDING, UH THEY NOW THEY CAN FOLD IT IN, THEY CAN
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:17.73,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,HAVE EQUIPMENT THAT'S EASIER TO MANAGE AND\NRUN AND USE AND MORE PROFITABLE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:22.37,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,ARE YOU SEEING UH TRACTION IN THE\NRESTORATION PROFESSIONALS?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:23.99,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,BIG TIME, BIG TIME.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:33.68,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,FOR EXAMPLE, WHEN I WAS AT THAT PANEL AT THE\NEXPERIENCE A COUPLE YEARS AGO AND I MENTIONED IT AND EVERYBODY SAID HVAC IS THE MOST IGNORED.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:37.95,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND THEN I CAME BACK WITH, KNOW, IT'S ALSO\NVERY IMPORTANT AND NEEDS TO BE DONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:40.41,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I COULD SEE THE HEADS NODDING IN THE\NAUDIENCE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:41.75,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,EVERYBODY KNOWS.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:43.16,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WE ALL KNOW THAT IT HAS TO BE DONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:45.24,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,GONNA SPEAK AGAIN AT THE EXPERIENCE, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:45.68,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THIS FALL.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:49.57,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WHAT'S THE TOPIC?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:51.29,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S AN EXCITING ONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:07:00.45,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AH IT'S IN REGARD TO A RESEARCH PAPER THAT\NWAS PUBLISHED BY THE CLEANING INDUSTRY RESEARCH INSTITUTE.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:05.90,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THEY HAVE A BIANNUAL JOURNAL THAT COMES OUT\NCALLED THE JOURNAL OF CLEANING SCIENCE.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:09.84,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND IT'S A VERY SERIOUS SCIENTIFIC UH\NJOURNAL.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:19.32,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND THE COVER STORY, THE COVER STORY OF THAT\NJOURNAL ACTUALLY IS A RESEARCH PAPER THAT COVERS EXACTLY WHAT WE'RE TALKING ABOUT, METHODOLOGIES OF HVAC CLEANING.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:20.10,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:22.04,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THE PRESENTATION IS GOING TO BE ON THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:33.76,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I'M GOING TO BE UH ON STAGE WITH JOHN MILES,\NWHO IS THE CHIEF SCIENCE OFFICER FOR SUPERSTRATUM, FANTASTIC COMPANY THAT MAKES MOLD DECONTAMINATION CHEMISTRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:41.57,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,HE'S ALSO HIS CAREER PRIOR TO THAT POSITION\NWAS IN THE FLEX DUCT MANUFACTURING SECTOR.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:47.21,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,HE WAS ACTUALLY ON THE TEAM THAT DESIGNED\NTHE VERY ADHESIVE WITH WHICH FLEX DUCTING IS MADE.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:49.11,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO YOU COULD SAY THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:56.17,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,OUT OF THIS MAN AND A HANDFUL OF OTHERS KNOW\NMORE ABOUT FLEX DUCT ADHESIVE THAN ANYBODY LITERALLY IN THE WORLD.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:59.58,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND I'M GOING TO BE HONORED BY SHARING THE\NSTAGE WITH HIM AT THIS PRESENTATION.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:01.32,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S GOING TO BE A REALLY COOL PRESENTATION.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.32,0:08:04.07,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,COULD JOIN UH OUR SERIES HERE AT ONE POINT?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:05.64,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'D BE NICE TO HAVE HIM ON.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:08.15,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AM CONFIDENT THAT I'VE ACTUALLY SPOKEN WITH\NHIM.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:10.05,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,HE'S EAGER TO DO SO,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:12.22,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,TERRIFIC, THAT'S TERRIFIC, THANK YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:13.30,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WELL, THAT'S GREAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:20.42,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WE SHOULD BE, UH THAT'S A LITTLE TEASER FOR\NWHAT'S COMING, BECAUSE IS IT PUBLISHED NOW OR IT'S SOON TO BE PUBLISHED OFFICIALLY?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:23.03,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,CAME OUT THIS, WHAT'S TODAY, FRIDAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:25.79,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT JUST CAME OUT FOUR DAYS AGO, YEAH.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:27.78,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT IS OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:30.12,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IN FACT, I DIDN'T EVEN KNOW IT HAD COME OUT\NYET.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:37.38,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I WAS WATCHING EVERY DAY TO SEE WHEN IT WAS\NGONNA COME OUT, BECAUSE I KNEW THAT THAT HAD MADE THE COVER STORY, AND I'M LIKE, OKAY, I GOTTA WATCH THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.58,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I GOT A PHONE CALL OUT OF THE BLUE FROM\NBARRY COSTA.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:42.53,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,HE SAID, CONGRATULATIONS, YOUR RESEARCH\NPAPER JUST CAME OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.53,0:08:45.51,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I'M LIKE, HOLY CRAP, THANKS, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.53,0:08:47.96,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YEAH.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:48.66,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THAT'S FANTASTIC.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:50.72,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,SO HE'S THE ONE THAT BROKE THE NEWS TO YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:52.20,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,YOU GOT IT FROM BARRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:54.20,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WELL, THAT'S FANTASTIC.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.05,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WELL, WE SHOULD START TALKING ABOUT THIS\NNEXT WEEK.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:09:01.37,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,MAYBE WE CAN START TO UNPACK THAT A LITTLE\NBIT MORE BECAUSE IT'S BIG NEWS.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:08.83,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S GOING TO BE A SEISMIC SHIFT IN HOW UH\NHVAC COMPANIES APPROACH UH HVAC LENDING.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:09.56,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,EXAGGERATION.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:15.54,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S ACTUALLY BEING CALLED THE MOST, UH THE\NBOMB, THE BIGGEST BOMB EVER DROPPED.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:16.46,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND NOT A BAD BOMB.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:17.34,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,I MEAN, IT'S A GOOD BOMB.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.72,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,IT'S AN INFORMATIONAL BOMB.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:20.02,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:25.85,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,UH THE BIGGEST INFORMATIONAL BOMB DROPPED ON\NTHE HVAC CLEANING INDUSTRY IN HISTORY.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:29.26,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,UM SO IT'S PRETTY COOL STUFF.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:31.99,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,WELL, I CAN'T WAIT TO TALK ABOUT IT WITH\NYOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:33.95,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,HAVE A GREAT MEMORIAL WEEKEND.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:39.26,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,ENJOY YOUR BOAT, ENJOY YOUR WEATHER AND LOOK\NFORWARD TO TALKING TO YOU NEXT WEEK ABOUT THE BOMB.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:40.51,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,AND YOU AS WELL, DAVE.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:41.50,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THANK YOU MUCH.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:42.16,TemplateSub,,0,0,0,,THANKS, DAVID.
